item.title: Directory Browsing
item.description: It is possible to view the directory listing. Directory listing may reveal hidden scripts, include files, backup source files, etc. which can be accessed to read sensitive information.

item.title: Directory Browsing
item.description: It is possible to view a listing of the directory contents. Directory listings may reveal hidden scripts, include files, backup source files, etc., which can be accessed to reveal sensitive information.
